    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284900/extras/461c94ee7d92042075295ff86260698f.avif?t=1747087531\" width=620 height=116 /></span><br><strong>ALIGNMENT</strong> is a challenging and engaging puzzle game that will put your logical reasoning skills to the test. By moving colored objects and placing them on their respective platforms, you will explore through a series of increasingly complex levels. With an average playtime of 1 hour, this game will challenge your ability to piece together various systems as you progress.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284900/extras/50759e46a29ab5b02b62b502cb688a45.avif?t=1747087531\" width=620 height=116 /></span><br><strong>ENDINGS:</strong> Your journey towards success will determine a specific and unique conclusion. Can you piece together clues and uncover all 5 possible endings?<br><br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284900/extras/d4e52b83635d2db3a13dc7bf6270c51d.avif?t=1747087531\" width=620 height=116 /></span><br><strong>THIS IS A CHALLENGING GAME:</strong> Alignment serves as a way to challenge your proficiency in unraveling complex and enigmatic systems and puzzles. By identifying patterns within the puzzles, you can gain a deeper insight into the system and establish a solid understanding of its underlying principles.<br><br><strong>DO NOT BE DISCOURAGED:</strong> During gameplay, there will be instances when using the <i>undo feature</i> becomes necessary. This doesn't imply that you've made a mistake in the puzzle. The <i>undo feature</i> is a vital game mechanic, not a reset button. Take advantage of the <i>undo tool</i> by exploring the end of the stage and experimenting with each machine. This approach will help you gain a deeper understanding of the game and enhance your overall experience.",
